<p>Bitcoin is a joke. Anonymous digits are not trustworthy as currency. Crypto-currencies invite criminality online and don’t work in the real economy. http://alfidicapitalblog.blogspot.com/2013/12/the-serious-disadvantages-of-bitcoin.html</p>

